OL,3,CFire chiefs call for urgent action on
OL,4,Cdrownings
OL,6,FFire chiefs are calling for urgent
OL,7,Fnational action to prevent drownings
OL,8,Fafter a 16-year-old boy died while
OL,9,Fswimming in a lake during a spell of
OL,10,Fhot weather.
OL,12,FThe National Fire Chiefs Council
OL,13,F(NFCC) has urged the Government to
OL,14,Fgive fire services in England a legal
OL,15,Fduty to respond to water emergencies,
OL,16,Fsuch as rescues in rivers, lakes and
OL,17,Fcanals.
