OL,3,CFire chiefs call for urgent action on
OL,4,Cdrownings
OL,6,FThe call comes during the NFCC's Be
OL,7,FWater Aware campaign and as emergency
OL,8,Fservices report a rise in water-
OL,9,Frelated incidents.
OL,11,FThe teenager died after getting into
OL,12,Fdifficulty at Colwick Country Park in
OL,13,FNottingham on Wednesday evening. His
OL,14,Fbody was recovered hours later.
