OL,3,CFire chiefs call for urgent action on
OL,4,Cdrownings
OL,6,FChief Inspector David Mather of
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police said: "While
OL,8,Fwork is now under way to understand
OL,9,Fhow the boy came into difficulty, I
OL,10,Fwould like to take this opportunity to
OL,11,Fhighlight this case as a reminder of
OL,12,Fthe devastating consequences of
OL,13,Fentering open water ` regardless of
OL,14,Fwhether people do so deliberately or
OL,15,Finadvertently."
OL,17,FTom Staples, from Nottinghamshire Fire
OL,18,Fand Rescue Service, said the incident
OL,19,Fwas a "stark reminder" of the hidden
OL,20,Fdangers in open water.
