OL,3,CFire chiefs call for urgent action on
OL,4,Cdrownings
OL,6,FThe NFCC says the lack of a legal duty
OL,7,Fin England means fire services face
OL,8,Flimits on how much they can invest in
OL,9,Fwater rescue training, equipment and
OL,10,Feducation. It also leads to
OL,11,Finconsistencies across the UK, with
OL,12,FWales having a statutory duty for
OL,13,Finland water rescue, and Scotland and
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland holding duties in
OL,15,Frelation to major flooding.
OL,17,FKirby said clearer responsibilities
OL,18,Ffor fire and rescue services, backed
OL,19,Fby law and funding, would help improve
OL,20,Femergency response and public safety
OL,21,Fcampaigns.
