OL,3,CFire chiefs call for urgent action on
OL,4,Cdrownings
OL,6,FFigures from the Water Incident
OL,7,FDatabase show 1,409 people died in
OL,8,Faccidental drownings between 2019 and
OL,9,F2023, with more than half in inland
OL,10,Fwaters.
OL,12,FThe NFCC also wants the Government to
OL,13,Fappoint a lead department or minister
OL,14,Ffor water safety to better coordinate
OL,15,Fprevention work.
OL,17,FTemperatures reached 29.3C at Kew
OL,18,FGardens in London on Thursday ` the
OL,19,Fhottest May 1 on record ` with fire
OL,20,Fservices warning of a surge in water
OL,21,Fincidents.
