OL,3,CFire chiefs call for urgent action on
OL,4,Cdrownings
OL,6,FThe London Fire Brigade said such
OL,7,Fincidents were up 32% last month.
OL,9,FAssistant Commissioner Patrick
OL,10,FGoulbourne said: "Even when the sun is
OL,11,Fshining, water temperatures can be
OL,12,Fdangerously cold."
OL,14,FThe RNLI urged swimmers to float on
OL,15,Ftheir backs if in trouble and to only
OL,16,Fswim at lifeguarded beaches.
